Trump ya ce Kavanaugh ya sha wahala daga mummunan hali da fushin Jam'iyyar Democrat
"Duk wani murya da aka yi wa Alkalin Kavanaugh, murya ce da ta yi watsi da dabarun da suka shafi 'yancin 'yan Adam", in ji Trump a wani taron da aka yi a Wheeling, West Virginia.
Trump ya bayyana cewa Kavanaugh ya sha wahala daga rashin tausayi da fushin jam'iyyar Democrat a lokacin da ya ke neman takararsa.
Kavanaugh ya shaida wa majalisa a ranar Alhamis, yana ƙin yarda da zargin da Christine Blaisey Ford ta yi game da cin zarafin jima'i da aka yi shekaru da yawa da suka wuce a lokacin da su biyun matasa ne.
Ford ya kuma yi shaida a lokacin da ake sauraron karar.
Shugaban ya bayyana a ranar Asabar cewa a yau jama'ar Amirka sun shaida hikimar Kavanaugh, ƙarfin hali da kuma halayensa.
"Duk wani murya da aka yi wa Alkalin Kavanaugh tana goyon bayan daya daga cikin manyan masana shari'a na wannan karni, wani babban lauya mai suna da kyakkyawan suna a cikin aikin jama'a", in ji shugaban a gaban taron magoya bayan West Virginia.
Shugaban kasa ya yi amfani da shi wajen ganin sunan Kavanaugh a matsayin babban takararsa yayin da yake magana game da muhimmancin kuri'un 'yan Republican a zaben.
"Akwai makonni biyar kafin daya daga cikin manyan zabuka na zamaninmu.
Duk da cewa ba ni ne mai neman takara ba, a gaskiya ni ma ina cikinsa, in ji Trump.
