Shugaba Donald Trump ya fara taron neman zabe a birnin Wheeling, West Virginia.
Wannan ne taro na farko a cikin tarurrukan Trump guda biyar da aka shirya, wanda ya hada da tsayawa a wurare da aka sani, ciki har da Tennessee da Mississippi.
Ta hanyar jinkirta zaben tabbatar da zabensa na cika wani wuri a kotun koli, Trump yana da niyyar tallafawa zaben da ke tafe a tsakiyar lokacin lokacinsa, saboda 'yan Republican suna cikin haɗarin rasa iko da majalisa a lokacin da za su yi zabe a watan Nuwamba.
A wane lokaci ne za a yi taron Trump a West Virginia a yau da dare, kuma ta yaya za ku iya kallon su a kan layi?
An shirya ziyarar Trump zuwa Wheeling, West Virginia, a karfe 7 na yammacin yammacin yau, Asabar, 29 ga Satumba, 2018.
Za ku iya kallon ziyarar Trump a Wheeling, West Virginia, a ƙasa ta hanyar watsa shirye-shiryen YouTube.
Trump zai yi la'akari da sauraron da aka yi a wannan makon game da babban kotun Burt Kavanaugh, wanda ya haifar da tashin hankali game da zargin lalata da ke riƙe da amincewar Majalisar Dattijai har mako guda kafin FBI ta gudanar da bincike.
Amma babban burin wannan taron na neman taimakon 'yan Republican su samu karfin gwiwa a zaben watan Nuwamba.
Saboda haka, a lokacin yakin neman zaben shugaban kasa Donald Trump, an sanar da cewa waɗannan tarurrukan biyar na mako mai zuwa suna da nufin "sake kunna masu sa kai da magoya baya" yayin da 'yan Republican ke ƙoƙarin karewa da faɗaɗa rinjayen su a Majalisar Dattawa da Majalisar Dattijai, a cewar Reuters.
"Sarrafawa a kan majalisa tana da muhimmanci sosai ga shirinsa, cewa shugaban zai ziyarci jihohi da yawa da zai iya, kuma muna fara wani lokacin yakin neman zabe mai cike da alkawuran", wani mai magana da yawun Trump ya shaida wa Reuters, wanda ya ƙi a ambaci.
Taron da aka shirya a Wesbanco Arena da ke Wheeling a yau zai iya kawo magoya bayan Ohio da Pennsylvania kuma ya jawo hankalin kafofin watsa labarai na Pittsburgh, a cewar West Virginia Metro News.
A ranar Asabar ne Trump zai ziyarci West Virginia, jihar da ya samu nasara sama da kashi 40 cikin 100 a shekarar 2016.
Trump yana kokarin taimaka wa dan takarar majalisar dattijai ta West Virginia, Patrick Morrissey, dan Republican, wanda ya yi watsi da binciken zamantakewa.
"Ba shi da kyau ga Morrissey cewa shugaban ya zo ya ba shi wani ci gaba a binciken zamantakewa", in ji Simon Heather, masanin siyasa a Jami'ar West Virginia, a cewar Reuters.
