Kasar Sin ta ce yawan mutanen da ke da cutar HIV da kuma cutar sankara ya karu da kashi 14 cikin 100.
Hukumar lafiya ta ce, mutane fiye da 820,000 ne suka kamu da cutar.
A cikin kwata na biyu na shekara ta 2018 kadai, an samu wasu sababbin shari'o'i 40,000.
Yawancin sababbin cututtuka sun fito ne daga jima'i, wanda ya nuna canji a baya.
A wasu wurare a ƙasar Sin, cutar ta kamu da cutar HIV da sauri ta wurin zubar da jini.
Amma, adadin mutanen da ke kamuwa da cutar HIV ta wannan hanyar ya ragu zuwa kusan sifili, in ji hukumar lafiya ta kasar Sin a wani taro a lardin Yunnan.
Duk da haka, a kowace shekara, adadin mutanen da suke rayuwa da HIV a ƙasar Sin yana ƙaruwa da 100,000.
Yada HIV ta hanyar jima'i babbar matsala ce a cikin al'ummar LGBT a kasar Sin.
A shekara ta 1997, an kawar da cin zarafin yin jima'i a kasar Sin, amma nuna bambanci ga mutane a cikin al'ummomin LGBT yana da yawa.
Bincike ya nuna cewa saboda ra'ayoyin banza, maza 70 zuwa 90 cikin 100 da suka yi jima'i da maza sun auri mata.
Yawancin cututtuka na cututtuka sun faru ne saboda rashin kariya a cikin waɗannan dangantaka.
