A garin da aka haifi firist na Anglican guda ɗaya da aka ba kyautar Victoria Cross domin yaƙin da ya yi a lokacin Yaƙin Duniya na Ɗaya, an yi bikin cika shekaru 100.
Lt. Col. Reverend Bernard Van ya lashe kyautar a ranar 29 ga Satumba, 1918, a hare-haren Bellenglise da Lehaucourt.
Bayan kwana huɗu, wani dan harbi ya kashe shi, ba tare da sanin cewa an ba shi lambar yabo mafi girma a Birtaniya ba.
