Ɗaya daga cikin jikokinsa, Michael Van, ya ce yana da matukar alama cewa an buɗe wannan abin tunawa daidai shekaru 100 bayan aikin kakansa wanda aka ba shi lambar yabo.
A ranar 29 ga Satumba, 1918, Lt. Col. Van ya jagoranci rundunarsa ta hanyar Canal de Saint-Quentin a cikin hazo mai yawa da kuma mummunan harbi daga bindigogi da bindigogi.
Daga baya, ya kai hari kan layin wuta kuma ya ja-goranci ƙungiyarsa da gaba gaɗi kafin ya kai wa bindigogi hari da hannu ɗaya kuma ya kashe uku daga cikin rukunin.
An kashe Lieutenant Colonel Van ne a ranar 4 ga Oktoba, 1918, wata guda kafin karshen yakin.
Michael Van, mai shekara 72, ya ce ayyukan kakansa suna da ban sha'awa, kuma na san ba zan taɓa yin hakan ba, amma hakan ya sa na kasance da tawali'u.
