Turai ta sake samun kambin gasar a gasar bayan tawagar da kyaftin din Denmark Thomas Björn ya jagoranta ta kai maki 14.5 da ake bukata don ta lashe gasar a Amurka.
Tauraron Amurka, Phil Mickelson, wanda ya yi rauni a mafi yawan gasar, ya jefa bugun farko na 16th hole (tare da par 3) a cikin ruwa, inda ya rasa wasan da Francesco Molinari.
Mai wasan golf na Italiya, Molinari, ya yi kyau sosai a duk zagaye, ya zama ɗaya daga cikin 'yan wasa hudu a tarihin gasar da suka kai ga daidaituwa 5-0-0, tun lokacin da aka gudanar da gasar a cikin tsarin yanzu bayan 1979.
Dan Amurka Jordan Spite ya ci gaba da cin nasara da 5 & 4 daga dan wasan Turai, wanda ke cikin mafi ƙasƙanci a cikin jerin  Torbjörn Olesen na Denmark.
Dustin Johnson, wanda ke jagorantar 'yan wasan duniya, ya ci nasara da 2 da 1 a hannun Ian Paulter na Ingila, wanda wannan zai zama wasan karshe na Ryder Cup.
Wani ɗan Spain mai suna Sergio Garcia, wanda ya shahara a gasar Ryder Cup a tsawon shekaru takwas, ya zama dan Turai mafi yawan maki a gasar a duk lokacin, yana ƙara yawan maki zuwa 25.5 a wannan shekara.
Ba na yawan kuka, amma yau ba zan iya kame kaina ba.
Shekara ce mai wuya.
Ina godiya sosai ga Thomas don ya gayyace ni kuma ya gaskata da ni.
Ina farin cikin sake ɗaga kofin.
"Abin da ya fi muhimmanci a gare ni shi ne tawagar, kuma ina farin cikin taimaka wa 'yan wasan da suka yi nasara a Turai".
Ya ba da tabbacin cewa ɗan'uwansa John Ram ya ci Tiger Woods da 2&1 a ranar Lahadi.
"Ina alfahari da cewa na ci Tiger Woods, amma na girma ina kallon sa a wasan", in ji Ram mai shekara 23.
Woods ya yi rashin nasara a wasanni hudu da ya buga a Faransa, kuma a yanzu haka, ya samu ci gaba da kasancewa a kan 13-21-3.
Wani labari mai ban mamaki game da daya daga cikin manyan 'yan wasa na dukan lokaci, wanda ya lashe manyan wasanni 14 a duniya, wanda ya fi Jack Nicklaus.
Ƙungiyar Amurka ta fuskanci matsaloli a duk ƙarshen mako, sai dai Patrick Reid, Justin Thomas da Tony Finau, waɗanda suka nuna golf mai kyau a duk kwanakin gasar.
Kamfanin Amurka Jim Furick ya ce bayan wasan da suka yi, "Ina alfahari da wadannan 'yan wasan, sun yi gwagwarmaya.
A wani lokaci da muke wannan safiya, mun matsa wa tawagar Turai.
Akwai wani yaki.
Ina sa Thomas ya yi kaciya.
Shi kyaftin ne mai kyau.
Duk 'yan wasan 12 da ya buga sun yi kyau sosai.
Za mu sake haɗuwa, mu tattauna muhimman al'amura da Ƙungiyar 'Yan Wasa ta Golf ta Amirka da kuma Kwamitinmu na Rider Cup, kuma mu ci gaba da yin tunani.
Ina ƙaunar waɗannan 'yan'uwa 12 kuma ina alfahari da kasancewa kyaftinansu.
Ba za ka iya yin watsi da maƙiyi ba.
Mun yi tsalle ne kawai.
Labari na Red Tide: Ƙarƙashin taro a Pinellas, Manatee da Sarasota
Rahoton da kwamitin kifi da namun daji na Florida ya fitar a kwanan nan ya nuna cewa yawan ruwan sama da ke jan ruwa a yankin Tampa Bay ya ragu.
A cewar kwamitin, akwai rahotanni game da yanayin da ake hana ci gaban a yankunan Pinellas, Manatee, Sarasota, Charlotte da Collier Counties  hakan yana nuna raguwar taro.
Ruwan ruwan da ke cike da ruwan sama mai launin ruwan kasa yana da nisan mil 130 a gabar tekun daga yankin Pinellas a arewa zuwa yankin Lee a kudu.
Ana iya ganin wuraren da ake samun algae a kusan mil 10 daga gabar tekun gundumar Hillsborough, amma sun fi ƙasa da na makon da ya gabata.
Ana ganin ruwan sama a gundumar Pasco.
A makon da ya gabata, an samu rahotanni na matsakaici a yankin bakin teku ko kuma a cikin ƙananan ciki a cikin Pinellas County, low zuwa high a cikin yankin bakin teku na Hillsborough County, yanayin da ake ciki na babban taro a Manatee County, yanayin da ake ciki na babban taro a cikin yankin bakin teku ko kuma a cikin Sarasota County, yanayin da ake ciki na matsakaici a cikin Charlotte County, yanayin da ake ciki na babban taro a cikin yankin bakin teku ko kuma a cikin yankin Librey County, da kuma ƙananan taro a cikin Cooley County.
Ana ci gaba da samun rahotanni game da ciwon huhu a Pinellas, Manatee, Sarasota, Lee, da Coolar Counties.
A makon da ya gabata, ba a samu rahoton kamuwa da cutar ta hanyar numfashi a arewa maso yammacin Florida ba.
